The reactions varied on that. Devil cuckled knowingly, James nodded in approval and Jacob&hellip; well he outright stared at her chest. Deziree couldn&rsquo;t avoid a chuckle herself.
&ldquo;So&hellip; this is really part of the whole package?&rdquo; Jacob asked. &ldquo;Just to clarify, I mean.&rdquo;
