&ldquo;Neither does being able to fly, yet here we are,&rdquo; Deziree interrupted. &ldquo;I know it&rsquo;s hard to understand, but we can see this energy and feel it inside our bodies. And it&rsquo;s more effective than fat cells alone would be.&rdquo;
