Now that was odd. Susan took a further look at the &lsquo;Angel&rsquo;s getup. Her black leotard seemed to be as good as new - albeit dirty now. And the ballerinas - considering the forces at play, these shoes should have flown off her feet long ago. How come they still stuck to them? And why didn&rsquo;t the &lsquo;Angel&rsquo; wear boots instead, unlike her she seems to have been super long enough to buy herself a pair. Susan figured that this was a trap.
