Susan looked up again. She had used precious seconds to stare her clothes that her enemy could have used to initiate an attack. If fact, Susan had fully expected her too and thus never lowered her defense. But the &lsquo;Angel&rsquo; was still locked in place, hovering above the skyline, arms crossed and with a confident smile.
