Susan began to laugh. &ldquo;You&rsquo;ve got to be kidding me! Kicking my ass? I&rsquo;ve got twice as much of this energy inside me than you have.&rdquo; She showed off her oversized biceps. &ldquo;And I am strong enough to shrug off anything you throw at me!&rdquo;
