Off course, the &lsquo;Angel&rsquo; dodged her attacks with ease. Susan knew that this would happen and kept punching and kicking the air, trying to read her opponents movements, to predict her next dodge. Eventually, she found an opening that she used to slam her fist right into the &lsquo;Angel&rsquo;s abdomen.
Boom.
