&ldquo;I don&rsquo;t really get it myself. Maybe it&rsquo;s because of his condition, but his apology sounded really sincere. I know it sounds naïve, but only time will tell if we really get back together or whether we&rsquo;re just prolonging the inevitable.&rdquo;
