Erika shook her head. &ldquo;I knew nothing about the whole affair.&rdquo; She took a sip from her drink. &ldquo;But the fact that he&rsquo;s so secretive about it narrows it down.&rdquo;
&ldquo;So you know what he&rsquo;s hiding from me?&rdquo;
